high_descs: Walk to the table to your right.
Grab the large knife on the table.
Turn around and walk to the stove to your left.
Place the knife in the large pan on the stove.
Grab the large pan with the knife inside.
Turn around and walk to the table to your right.
Place the large pan with the knife inside on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a knife inside it on the white table.

high_descs: Go forward, turn right, go forward to the right side of the table.
Take the large knife to the left of the spatula from the table.
Turn around, go forward, turn left, go forward to the oven.
Put the knife in the pot on the left of the stove top.
Take the pot from the stove top.
Turn around, go forward, turn right to the white table. Go to the table.
Put the pot to the left of the fork on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a knife in it on a table.

high_descs: Move forward and turn to the right and face the white table.
Pick up the knife from the back of the table.
Carry the knife and turn around, then left to move to the stove.
Place the knife inside the pot on the left front burner.
Pick up the pot from the front left burner.
Carry the pot and turn around and then face right to the white table.
Place the pot on the white table, to the right of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife and pot to a table.
